content:
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 17 ยง 79.28 - Vehicles to yield right-of-way to aircraft

State Regulations

All vehicles in or upon the airport, shall yield the
right-of-way to any and all aircraft in motion. However, emergency vehicles
shall have right-of-way over taxiing aircraft. Notes
